		"description": {
			"value": "<p><strong>Action</strong> - Nearby Allies (30 ft) - Channel Divinity - Magical</p><p>You expend a use of your @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.WKKAHUBp42287xui]{Channel Divinity} feature. You can't use this feature on a &amp;reference[construct]{construct}.</p><ul><li><p>You restore a number of hit points equal to five times your cleric level and divide those hit points among any creatures of your choice within 30 ft., though you cannot bring a creature above half their hit points with this feature.</p></li></ul>",
